<section class="ptb-100">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="main-content-text">

            <!-- Section 1: Respect and Dignity -->
            <h3>1. Respect and Dignity:</h3>
            <p>Treat all users with respect and dignity. Do not engage in discriminatory, harassing, or abusive behavior. Remember that our community is diverse, and everyone deserves to be treated with kindness and consideration.</p>
        
            <div class="gap-20"></div>
        
            <!-- Section 2: Privacy and Confidentiality -->
            <h3>2. Privacy and Confidentiality:</h3>
            <p>Respect the privacy and confidentiality of other users' health information. Do not share or disclose personal health information of others without their explicit consent. Be mindful of the sensitivity of health-related discussions and ensure that any shared information is done so with the utmost care.</p>
        
            <div class="gap-20"></div>
        
            <!-- Section 3: Compliance with Laws -->
            <h3>3. Compliance with Laws:</h3>
            <p>Abide by all applicable laws and regulations related to healthcare and privacy. Do not engage in any activities that violate the law or our Terms and Conditions. It is essential to understand and comply with local, national, and international regulations governing healthcare and online conduct.</p>
        
            <div class="gap-20"></div>
        
            <!-- Section 4: Professionalism -->
            <h3>4. Professionalism:</h3>
            <p>Maintain a professional and courteous tone in all interactions. Refrain from posting inappropriate, offensive, or misleading content. Remember that this platform is designed to foster positive health discussions and support. Professionalism is key to creating a safe and constructive environment for everyone.</p>
        
            <div class="gap-20"></div>
        
            <!-- Section 5: Security -->
            <h3>5. Security:</h3>
            <p>Protect your account credentials and report any unauthorized access. Do not attempt to hack, disrupt, or compromise the security of the app. Security is crucial for maintaining the trust of our users, and any attempt to compromise the integrity of the platform will be taken seriously and dealt with promptly.</p>
        
            <div class="gap-20"></div>
        
            <!-- Section 6: Feedback and Reporting -->
            <h3>6. Feedback and Reporting:</h3>
            <p>Provide constructive feedback to help us improve the app. Report any inappropriate behavior or content promptly. Your feedback is valuable in enhancing the user experience and addressing any issues that may arise. Reporting inappropriate behavior helps us maintain a safe and supportive community.</p>
        
            <div class="gap-20"></div>
        
            <!-- Section 7: Collaboration -->
            <h3>7. Collaboration:</h3>
            <p>Collaborate with healthcare professionals and other users in a positive and constructive manner. Foster a supportive community for health and wellness. Collaboration is at the heart of our platform, and by working together respectfully, we can create a space where users feel empowered to share their experiences and knowledge for the benefit of all.</p>
        
            <div class="gap-20"></div>
        
            <!-- Section 8: Violation Consequences -->
            <h3>8. Violation Consequences:</h3>
            <p>Violation of this Code of Conduct may result in the suspension or termination of your account. We take these guidelines seriously to ensure the well-being of our community. Consequences for violations are implemented to maintain a healthy and secure environment for all users.</p>
        
        </div>
        
    </div>
</section>
